%% Shop onboarding state machine (PrintHub).  Render at https://mermaid.live
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft
    Draft --> PendingReview: submit application
    PendingReview --> Active: admin approve (owner elevated)
    PendingReview --> Rejected: admin reject (reason)
    Rejected --> PendingReview: revise & resubmit
    Active --> Suspended: admin suspend (reason)
    Suspended --> Active: admin reinstate
    note right of Suspended
        Hidden from search; in-progress
        orders continue to completion.
    end note
